    C -->|Quit to Menu| A

    B -->|Player Lands on Property| D[Property Popup]
    D -->|Buy Property| B
    D -->|Cancel| B

    B -->|End Turn| F[Turn Banner Transition]
    F -->|Next Player Ready| B
